00:10:19,890 --> 00:10:25,830
Occasionally, whenever I came here, my heart was troubled.

56
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:37,430
After my Mother passed away...

57
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:42,730
I don't think I grew up at all.

58
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,220
I pretended to be strong,

59
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:51,390
but I couldn't overcome anything by myself.

60
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:55,810
I was just always weak. I think.

61
