00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:11,250
♫   Your fair face, your pure eyes  ♫

258
00:41:11,250 --> 00:41:12,840
♫   make my heart beat again   ♫

259
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:17,930
I love you.

260
00:41:17,930 --> 00:41:24,210
♫   Your warm hands, your voice calling me...  ♫

261
00:41:24,210 --> 00:41:25,760
I love you.

262
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:29,170
♫  Feels like an embrace  ♫

263
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:35,790
♫  My beautiful love   ♫

264
00:41:35,790 --> 00:41:42,050
♫   My one love that makes my heart flutter   ♫

265
00:41:42,050 --> 00:41:45,630
♫   That kind of person to me   ♫

266
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:53,490
♫   When the rain falls again, the one who'll fair it with me   ♫

